This folder contains files for short (15 minute) tutorials on data visualization in R using ggplot2.

There are four tutorials:

 - Scatter-plots ([code](https://github.com/chrishanretty/dataviz/blob/main/01_democratization/example.R), [video](https://youtu.be/rNhAP8dS0p0), [slides](http://chrishanretty.co.uk/dataviz/01_democratization/example.html))
 - bar charts ([code](https://github.com/chrishanretty/dataviz/blob/main/02_candidacy/example.R), [video](https://youtu.be/1ndGY-SBLqI), [slides](http://www.chrishanretty.co.uk/dataviz/02_candidacy/example.html))
 - plots with dates ([code](https://github.com/chrishanretty/dataviz/blob/main/03_datetime/example.R), [video](https://youtu.be/vEwRnx3yxa0), [slides](http://www.chrishanretty.co.uk/dataviz/03_datetime/example.html))
 - box-plots ([code](https://github.com/chrishanretty/dataviz/blob/main/04_boxplots/example.R), [video](https://youtu.be/hQLA8zxkfPU), [slides](http://www.chrishanretty.co.uk/dataviz/04_boxplots/example.html))
